\pard\plain \tx0\tx360\tx720\tx1080\tx1440\tx1800\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\sa360\sl264\slmult1\ltrch\loch {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Phew! We\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92ve now covered all major features of Scrivener. If you haven\u8217\'92t done so already, then soon you are going to want to create your own project and get writing. Generally you will want to create a separate Scrivener project for each writing project. }{\f0\fs24\b0 Additionally, each time a project is closed, Scrivener creates a full backup of the project. Check out }{\field{\*\fldinst HYPERLINK "scrivlnk://F02A8186-DF6D-4CD4-8F00-3C2804688F0A"}{\fldrslt\f0\fs24\b0 Backing Up}}{\f0\fs24\b0  for details on how to modify the settings to best suit your work style.}{ }
